'''斯諾登登山鐵路'''（Snowdon Mountain Railway）是位於[[英國|英國]][[威爾斯|威爾斯]]西北部[[格溫內斯|格溫內斯]]威爾斯最高峰[[斯諾登山|斯諾登山]]的一條登山鐵路<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.star-attractions.co.uk/attractions/snowdon_mountain/snowdon_mountain.htm |title=Tourist Attractions in Snowdonia Wales - Visit Snowdon Mountain Railway! |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20030415135300/http://www.star-attractions.co.uk/attractions/snowdon_mountain/snowdon_mountain.htm |archivedate=2003-04-15 }}</ref>。斯諾登登山鐵路全長7.6公里（4.7英里），起點是[[蘭貝里斯|蘭貝里斯]]，終點是斯諾登山的山頂。斯諾登登山鐵路也是英國唯一的一條公共登山鐵路<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.aboutbritain.com/SnowdonMountainRailway.htm |title=Snowdon Mountain Railway on AboutBritain.com |accessdate=2016-09-09 |archive-date=2016-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161001210643/http://www.aboutbritain.com/SnowdonMountainRailway.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
